00:02.001 --> 00:03.003
[grunts]

00:11.185 --> 00:12.316
Whoa.

00:15.102 --> 00:16.494
Ow.

00:16.581 --> 00:18.496
Damn it.

00:18.583 --> 00:19.932
[groans]

00:21.195 --> 00:22.152
[screams]

00:27.853 --> 00:29.725
Ah...

00:29.812 --> 00:31.161
Help!

00:31.248 --> 00:32.858
Mom!

00:32.945 --> 00:35.644
Anybody?!

00:35.731 --> 00:37.646
♪ Jump, jump♪

00:37.733 --> 00:39.474
